---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SubHero from '../components/SubHero.astro';
import Heading from '../components/Heading.astro';
import Eyebrow from '../components/Eyebrow.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout active="about" title="About"
  description="Caring Hearts Care was born from one family’s search for compassionate, reliable home care — a journey of love and dedication that became a promise to other families.">
  <SubHero
    title="About Us"
    crumbs={[{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'About Us' }]} />

  {/* Founder */}
  <section class="band band--cream">
    <div class="wrap about-founder">
      <div class="about-founder__media">
        <div class="about-founder__photo" style="background-image:url(/assets/photos/caregiver-couch.jpg)" role="img" aria-label="A nurse sitting on a couch holding an elderly client’s hand"></div>
        <div class="about-founder__plate">
          <span class="eyebrow">Co-Founder</span>
          <b>Nathalie Massey</b>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-founder__body">
        <Eyebrow tick>Meet the Founder</Eyebrow>
        <h2 class="about-founder__title">A Journey of Love and Dedication</h2>
        <p>In a world of uncertainties, one thing remains constant – the unwavering bond of family. For me, this truth hit home with profound clarity when my mother suffered two life-altering strokes seven years ago. Suddenly, the simple act of finding adequate care for her became an arduous challenge, laden with stress and anxiety.</p>
        <p>I intimately understand the profound struggles and emotional turmoil that accompany the role of a caregiver. The fear of entrusting our loved ones into the hands of strangers, the relentless worry of not being there when they need us the most – these are the burdens we carry, the silent battles we fight every day.</p>
        <p>It was amidst this backdrop of personal upheaval that Caring Hearts Care was born. As an accountant by trade, I never imagined myself venturing into the realm of home care. But life had other plans for me. Faced with the daunting task of finding compassionate and reliable caregivers for my mother, I embarked on a journey that would forever change my perspective.</p>
        <p>Driven by a burning desire to ease the burdens of families like mine, I made it my mission to create a haven of compassion and support. At Caring Hearts Care, we don’t just provide a service; we offer solace, understanding, and a genuine connection.</p>
        <p>Every caregiver we welcome into our family is not only rigorously licensed but also chosen for their unwavering passion and dedication to their calling. They are more than just employees; they are the extended arms of our clients’ families, offering love, empathy, and companionship in times of need.</p>
        <p>I know that nothing can truly replace the love and care of a family member. But I am committed to creating the closest semblance of it. I want every client’s family to rest easy, knowing that their loved ones are in the gentle, capable hands of caregivers who treat them with the same tenderness and devotion as their own kin.</p>
        <p>At Caring Hearts Care, we believe that compassion is not just a virtue but a way of life. We are here to walk alongside you, to lighten your load, and to ensure that every moment spent with us is filled with warmth and comfort. Because when it comes to caring for your loved ones, nothing matters more than a heart that beats with love.</p>
        <blockquote class="about-quote">
          &ldquo;Treating your family like ours, because we’ve faced the struggle of finding the right care too.&rdquo;
          <cite>&mdash; Nathalie M.</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Pledge band */}
  <section class="band band--navy">
    <div class="wrap pledge">
      <div class="pledge__media">
        <div class="pledge__photo" style="background-image:url(/assets/photos/pledge.jpg)" role="img" aria-label="A caregiver holding the hand of a senior client"></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <Heading onDark eyebrow="Our Pledge" title="The Caring Hearts Pledge: Your Family Is Our Family" />
        <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.86);line-height:var(--leading-normal);max-width:48ch;">
          At Caring Hearts Care, we promise to treat your family with the same love and dedication we’d give our own. Having sought these services for our loved ones, we understand the challenge of finding just the right caregiver. It’s our commitment to ensure you never feel alone in this journey, providing the compassionate, personalized care your family deserves.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top:1.6rem;">
          <Button variant="primary" href="/services">Discover More</Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
